    <section_number>25A</section_number>
    <catch_line>Display Of National Flag</catch_line>
    <order_by>25A</order_by>
    <text>
        In any city or town which accepts this section by vote of its city council or selectmen, the national flag shall be displayed at each polling place during the hours when voting is taking place thereat.
    </text>
